sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Cluster Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DSCCtrl as DataScienceCluster<br/>Controller
    participant DSCICtrl as DSCInitialization<br/>Controller
    participant FS as /opt/manifests<br/>(Local Filesystem)
    participant SecGen as SecretGenerator<br/>Controller
    participant Feature as Feature System<br/>(pkg/feature)
    participant SM as Service Mesh<br/>Operator
    participant KN as Knative<br/>Serving
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant AM as Alertmanager<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PD as PagerDuty<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DMS as DeadMansSnitch<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Admin,DMS: Flow 1: Platform Initialization
    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create DSCInitialization CR
    K8sAPI->>DSCICtrl: Watch event (TLS 1.2+, SA token)
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create namespaces<br/>(redhat-ods-applications,<br/>redhat-ods-monitoring)
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicies
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create user Groups<br/>(rhods-admins, rhods-users)

    Note over Admin,DMS: Flow 2: Component Deployment
    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create DataScienceCluster CR<br/>(enable components)
    K8sAPI->>DSCCtrl: Watch event (TLS 1.2+, SA token)
    DSCCtrl->>FS: Read component manifests<br/>(/opt/manifests/{component})
    FS-->>DSCCtrl: Kustomize manifests
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply rendered manifests<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Resources created

    Note over Admin,DMS: Flow 3: Service Mesh Config (KServe)
    DSCICtrl->>Feature: Load feature templates
    Feature->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMeshControlPlane CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    K8sAPI->>SM: Reconcile SMCP
    Feature->>K8sAPI: Create KnativeServing CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    K8sAPI->>KN: Reconcile KnativeServing
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create FeatureTracker CR

    Note over Admin,DMS: Flow 4: Monitoring Setup (Managed RHOAI)
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create monitoring Secrets<br/>(prometheus-proxy, alertmanager-proxy)
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Deploy Prometheus + Alertmanager<br/>via Kustomize manifests
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Routes (reencrypt TLS)
    Prom->>K8sAPI: Scrape ServiceMonitor targets
    AM->>PD: Alert escalation<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    AM->>DMS: Dead man's switch<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Admin,DMS: Flow 5: Secret Generation (OAuth)
    SecGen->>K8sAPI: Watch annotated Secrets
    SecGen->>K8sAPI: Generate random secret data
    SecGen->>K8sAPI: Create OAuthClient CR<br/>for Dashboard authentication
